    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Timetable for the Academic year of the college",
          "name": "Sanchit  Dongre",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Supportive faculty and rest of the staff including the lab staff",
          "name": "Sanchit  Dongre",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Events are well organised and committees of different groups like arts, dance ,singing, entrepreneurship",
          "name": "Sanchit  Dongre",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "TEC offers various technical and cultural festivals, such as 'AVALON' and 'Resonance,' providing platforms for students to showcase their talents and engage in extracurricular activities. The presence of clubs like the TEC ROBO Club fosters .",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "commutation to college is easy , its just 5 min walk from nerul station",
          "name": "Kartik shukla",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "The food of canteen is decent as per the price",
          "name": "Supranshu singh",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "The second thing I like in this college is there are no ragging issues by any seniors",
          "name": "Hrishikesh Rajbhar",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "There is a library where you can use your laptop for studying and even rent some books free for one week.",
          "name": "Chinmay Kalgutkar",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Classroom are too nice, all are digital classroom",
          "name": "Dhananjay Uddhav Jadhav",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Complete freedom to student, no stress on attending every lecture",
          "name": "Prasad",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Some the labs need renovation and upgradation",
          "name": "Sanchit  Dongre",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Limited Placement Opportunities The average placement package is between 3-5 lakh INR, which is lower than expected. The college could enhance its efforts to secure better opportunities for students, especially in core engineering sectors.",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Campus Life While there are some events and clubs, the overall campus life is not very vibrant, and social interactions could be more enriching with better-organized activities.",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Faculty replacements are not available. Once a faculty leaves, it's difficult to get a new one in less time.",
          "name": "Kunjal Mahajan",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "gymkhana is not upto the mark , college had a good stationary shop but its closed from around a year , hence printing documents becomes a hectic task",
          "name": "Kartik shukla",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Some College staff are not helping in studies, they just come and teach their syllabus",
          "name": "Supranshu singh",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college has a turf for playing games but they only allow for once in a week for only 1 hour.",
          "name": "Chinmay Kalgutkar",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Canteen is not good, I am not saying it is too bad but it was bad as compared to all other things in available in college.",
          "name": "Dhananjay Uddhav Jadhav",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Need of more capable wifi internet ???? service to students, yes there currently available it but it not work properly it don't have much more speed.",
          "name": "Dhananjay Uddhav Jadhav",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Canteen as it is a subjective thing it is all about personal taste",
          "name": "jayveersinh baldevsinh jadeja",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        }
      ]
    },
